Course Objectives:
In this project we will focus on the following objectives:


•	Objective 1: Automate HR tasks to enhance efficiency.
•	Objective 2: Ensure secure and accurate management of employee data.
•	Objective 3: Provide a user-friendly interface for easy navigation.

By the end of this project you will be able to learn :
•	Web Development: Build a full-stack app using Django, with front-end and back-end integration.
•	Database Management: Design databases and manage data using Django ORM.
•	Security: Implement user authentication and role-based access.
•	Project Management: version control, and documentation.
•	Problem-Solving: Analyze requirements, debug, and test thoroughly.
•	Real-World Applications: Understand business needs, improve communication, and work collaboratively.

You will deploy the project on the Nimbus Platform using Heroku or render or any other tools / platforms

